OL,3,CLove is in the air for couples eloping
OL,4,Cto Gretna Green
OL,6,FOnce known as the place that runaway
OL,7,Flovers would elope to, Gretna Green is
OL,8,Fstill seen as one of the most romantic
OL,9,Fplaces to get married by many around
OL,10,Fthe world.
OL,12,FIt became the place for young couples
OL,13,Fto get married after the 1754 Marriage
OL,14,FAct was introduced in England and
OL,15,FWales.
OL,17,FThe Law meant you couldn't marry
OL,18,Fwithout your parents' permission
OL,19,Funless you were over 21.
