OL,6,FThe laws in Scotland were less strict,
OL,7,Fand so the little village on the
OL,8,FScottish border became world-famous as
OL,9,Fa place for young couples to rebel and
OL,10,Felope.
OL,12,FYou can still get married in many of
OL,13,Fits historic buildings including the
OL,14,FFamous Blacksmith Shop.
OL,16,FSusan Houston is the director of
OL,17,FGretna Green Ltd., her family have
OL,18,Fbeen hosting weddings in three of the
OL,19,Fvillage's historic venues for five
OL,20,Fgenerations.
