OL,6,F"They're here for a reason coming
OL,7,Foften their two selves and we're
OL,8,Fproviding witnesses for them.
OL,10,F"It's many couples that just want a
OL,11,Fday themselves taking in the
OL,12,Fatmosphere the romance, reading about
OL,13,Fthe history and just being in this
OL,14,Flittle cottage of a building."
OL,16,FMany couples travelled Gretna Green to
OL,17,Ftie the knot on the most romantic day
OL,18,Fof the year.
OL,20,FOne of those couples was Amy and Grant
OL,21,FBalcombe.
