OL,6,FAfter nine years together, Amy booked
OL,7,Ftheir wedding in the Famous Blacksmith
OL,8,FShop and broke the news to Grant as
OL,9,Fthe clock struck midnight on New
OL,10,FYear's Eve.
OL,12,FShe said" "I've always thought about
OL,13,FGretna Green and then I started to
OL,14,Flook more into it and I just fell in
OL,15,Flove with it, it's just a dream.
OL,17,F"Just look at the romance, it's so
OL,18,Fromantic this place you look at the
OL,19,Fhistory that it's got behind it and I
OL,20,Fjust think it was right for us wasn't
OL,21,Fit", Grant added.
